description: Dexter is back and we want to give him exactly what he wants…that’s where Frankie comes in to give Dexter a great welcome fuck. “I’ll treat you right, don’t worry about it.” We had to ask, “You’re gonna wreck him, huh?” “Oh, he already knows…” Dexter was kind of nervous, considering the rumors he heard about Frankie’s rough play, but on that same note, he was very excited to try him out. Needless to say, he took it like a champ, and I think it’s safe to assume he really enjoyed it!
title: Frankie & Dexter: Bareback
